William Russell (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Russell_(actor) 0 William Russell Enoch (born 19 November 1924), better known as William Russell, is an English actor. He played the role of companion Ian Chesterton in Doctor Who, from the show's first episode in 1963 until 1965.
